This paper discusses the use of AI in multiple domains, such as criminal justice and consumer finance, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also focuses on the need for transparency and explainability in AI systems, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Software Engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
